void TKEY_16BitCounterClockConfig ( TKEY_TK16S_CLK_Enum  Sel)

Configure the touch key 16-bit counter clock source.

Parameters:
Sel,:Specify the 16-bit counter clock source. This parameter can be one of the following values:
  • TKEY_TK16S_CLK_0 : TKCLK/16.
  • TKEY_TK16S_CLK_1 : TKCLK/32.
  • TKEY_TK16S_CLK_2 : TKCLK/64.
  • TKEY_TK16S_CLK_3 : TKCLK/128.
Return values:
None

Parameters:

FlagStatus TKEY_GetFlagStatus ( u32  TKEY_Flag)

Check whether the specified TKEY flag has been set or not.

Parameters:
TKEY_Flag,:specify the flag that is to be check. This parameter can be one of the following values:
  • TKEY_FLAG_TKBUSY : Touch Key busy flag
  • TKEY_FLAG_TKCFOV : Touch Key 16-bit C/F counter overflow flag
  • TKEY_FLAG_TK16OV : Touch Key 16-bit counter overflow flag
  • TKEY_FLAG_TKRCOVF : 8-bit time slot counter overflow flag
  • TKEY_FLAG_TKTHF : Touch Key threshold match flag

ControlStatus  NewState 
)
